      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Up for sale is a vehicle in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find for any discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine, free of any scratches, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that looks and smells like new and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in top-tier shape, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history, ensuring a smooth and powerful driving experience that feels straight off the dealership floor.",
